📘 DreamVerse – Part 1 Foundation Summary

🌸 Game Identity

Game Name: DreamVerse

Genre:

- 🌍 Open World
- 🏡 Life Simulator
- 👥 Roleplay
- 🚗 Driving
- 🏠 Home Design
- 😌 Peaceful
- 🌎 Social
- 🎨 Creative

Main Motto:

«"A peaceful world where you can do anything you want."»

---

🌍 World Concept

DreamVerse ek bahut bada open world hoga.

Iske andar:

- 🏙 Cities
- 🏡 Villages
- 🏖 Beaches
- 🌲 Forests
- ⛰ Mountains
- ❄ Snow Areas
- 🏜 Desert
- 🌸 Flower Fields
- 🌊 Rivers & Lakes

Sab ek hi world ka hissa honge.

⭐ Secret Areas

Normal map ke alawa hidden places bhi honge:

- ☁ Sky Island
- 🌊 Underwater City
- 🌈 Rainbow Island
- 🌳 Magical Forest
- 🏔 Hidden Valley
- 🌌 Secret Cave

Rule:

- Yahan enemies nahi honge.
- Exploration based rewards milenge.

