- Clothes
- Decorations
- Furniture
- Vehicles
- Phone Theme
- Emotes
- Culture Items

---

🏡 Houses & Property System (Final)

House Types

Har area ka apna style hoga.

Examples:

- City Houses
- Village Houses
- Beach Houses
- Forest Cabins
- Mountain Houses
- Snow Houses
- Desert Houses

Secret Houses

Sirf secret areas me milenge.

Examples:

- Cloud House
- Giant Tree House
- Underwater House
- Volcano House
- Rainbow House

Har secret area me:

- Secret NPC
- Secret Furniture
- Secret Decorations
- Secret Vehicles

---

Plot System

- Basic plots free honge.
- Premium plots game currency se milenge.
- Plot lene ke baad player apna ghar khud design karega.

---

Building Freedom

Player:

- Furniture kahin bhi rakh sakta hai.
- Wall paint change kar sakta hai.
- Floor change kar sakta hai.
- Roof change kar sakta hai.
- Garden bana sakta hai.
- Swimming Pool bana sakta hai.
- Garage bana sakta hai.

Rule:
Dusre player ke ghar ko permission ke bina edit nahi kar sakta.

---

Build With Friends

Owner permissions decide karega.

Example:

✅ Furniture Place

✅ Furniture Remove

✅ Paint Walls

✅ Garden Decorate

✅ Build House

❌ Sell House

❌ Delete House

---

Memory Wall

Har ghar me Photo Album / Memory Wall ho sakti hai.

Player:

- Photos le sakta hai.
- Frames me laga sakta hai.
- Memories save kar sakta hai.

